### Create Article
POST http://localhost:4000/author-api/articles
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "author": "69afebdb7e1e8174f515e463",
  "title": "java",
  "category": "prog",
  "content": "java.util.*"
}

### Get Articles of Author
GET http://localhost:4000/author-api/articles/69afebdb7e1e8174f515e463

### Update Article
PUT http://localhost:4000/author-api/articles/69afec7b0cbfd32ae13939d2
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "author": "69afec7b0cbfd32ae13939d2",
  "title": "python",
  "category": "prog",
  "content": "functions, numpy, pandas"
}

### Delete Article
DELETE http://localhost:4000/author-api/users/69ae9554ad6ad394d7d3047b/articles/69ae9554ad6ad394d7d3047b

### Get All Articles (User)
GET http://localhost:4000/user-api/articles

### Logout
GET http://localhost:4000/common-api/logout

### Test API
GET http://localhost:4000/test

### Delete User (Admin)
DELETE http://localhost:4000/admin-api/users/

### Get All Users (Admin)
GET http://localhost:4000/admin-api/users/

### Delete Article (Alternative Route)
DELETE http://localhost:4000/author-api/articles/author-id/article-id

### Add Comment to Article
PUT http://localhost:4000/author-api/articles/author-id/article-id
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "comment": "good article"
}